Message-ID: <DM5PR1201MB25053E562DE3E53C1B95E506FF4B0@DM5PR1201MB2505.namprd12.prod.outlook.com>

Hi Erik,

Thanks for noticing this. The landing pages update every 20 minutes but because the builds only occur once a day the package version on the page only change once a day.

Yesterday the build script that generates the list of packages to be propagated (i.e., versions have been bumped) took longer than expected. This meant the next script didn't know which packages to push to master.bioconductor.org. This was a hiccup and did not happen with today's builds. Version 0.99.3 was propagated and is now on master.bioconductor.org.

I've re-run the script that generates the landing pages and we now see 0.99.3:

http://www.bioconductor.org/packages/3.6/bioc/html/seqCAT.html


Valerie


