On 10/14/2017 11:05 AM, Stian L?gstad wrote:
> Hi,
> 
> What should the NEWS file look like? Are there guidelines somewhere?

the basic requirement is that it be parsed by util::news(); using an 
'Rd' format is most robust.

A couple of examples include

